WRITING.TITLE: Fastest way to record and upload videos to file sharing site, such as Box
WRITING.TEXT:
I am a private violin teacher who has recorded lessons with students and burned them onto CDs in the past, but would like to switch to digitizing lesson videos. What would be the fastest way to record and upload video to an online sharing site? Specifications are: -Using a Mac -Very fast internet speed (~70 mbs download, ~50 mbs upload) -Videos would be around an hour long -Would prefer if video transfer would take no more than 10 minutes (time between lessons) -Good quality video (720p)
Thanks!
